# Metasploitable Lab 4 — Web Enumeration, WebDAV Exploitation, and Privilege Escalation

## Objective

The objective of this lab was to identify and exploit a vulnerable web service on the target system, gain remote command execution through a web application, establish a reverse shell, and escalate privileges to root.

This lab demonstrates a full attack chain from initial access to full system compromise.

---

