| Component | Description |
|-----------|-------------|
| Host Machine | MacBook Pro (Intel, 16GB RAM) |
| Virtualization | VirtualBox |
| Attacker Machine | Kali Linux |
| Target Machine | Metasploitable 2 |
| Network | VirtualBox Host-only Network |
